{"tid":1176488,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"好媽媽形象遭質疑 張栢芝被譏為大話精","createTime":"2019-05-29T09:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T11:22:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2462b4a2b6f257383c73914e7f34838fd3dded2b","tid":1176488,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559104436_e6b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559104436_e6b9.jpg&h=0677fc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛踏入39歲的失婚張栢芝，跟前夫謝霆鋒育有兩子Lucas和Quintus，去年11月誕下孻仔Marcus，但生父身份成謎，三名兒子都是跟栢芝生活，多年來建立好媽媽形象的栢芝，最近亮相大陸綜藝節目《天天向上》時，卻答不出兒子喜歡的菜名，隨之有網民翻摷番栢芝受訪時曾說過的話，跟現實中的她作出對比，揭發栢芝疑謊話連篇，被網民譏為「大話精」。<br />\n<br />\n事緣栢芝在節目上接受大張偉訪問，她表示小時候爸爸是廚師，由於受到爸爸的影響，自己從小就喜歡做菜，每天都會做兩道不同的菜給兒子吃，當大張偉問：「那分別喜歡甚麽菜？」栢芝卻答非所問，只說大兒子喜歡中餐，二兒子喜歡西餐，由於場面尷尬，同場的大陸女星李湘代為解釋：「大張偉說的是你給兒子燒的兩個甚麼菜？」栢芝答：「Lucas喜歡白米飯，Quintus喜歡漢堡包。」<br />\n<br />\n由於栢芝到最後都沒答出菜名，網民狠批：「圓都圓不回來，隨便說兩菜也行啊」、「看來平時真的沒做過飯了」、「隔着屏幕都能感到尷尬」、「她到底是真好媽媽還是撒謊精？」結果「撒謊精」三字一出，很多網民加入討論，大家都偵探柯南上身，翻出過往栢芝的訪問內容作對比，發現栢芝在《天》節目上說：「我自己就喜歡蔬菜，因為我天生喜歡吃素，我是從來沒有吃過肉的。」但過往她跟曹格亮相另一節目時，就曾即場吃曹格做的鍋包肉，又曾在社交網貼冬菇蒸雞開飯相，質疑她講大話。<br />\n<br />\n網民更揭發她還有很多驚人語錄，如：「連續流產了4次，才有了Quintus」、「拍戲3個月不睡覺」、「連睡16天」、「越不洗臉皮膚越好」、「越吃消夜就越瘦」等，認為她的言論太浮誇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559103908_53b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559103908_53b2.jpg&h=42fa55a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559104436_e6b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559104436_e6b9.jpg&h=0677fc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559103905_9e54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559103905_9e54.jpg&h=6b9a7429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559103902_c02c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559103902_c02c.jpg&h=e8472dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190529/large/1559104646_1429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190529%2Flarge%2F1559104646_1429.jpg&h=75fcd83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190529/59653183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59653183&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LqFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=6b56e645\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190529%2F59653183&h=da8fc62f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190529/59653183</a><br />\n<br />\n一人一個聽過最離譜既大話<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1176026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1176026</a>"},{"pid":"1691f19a7fc2a3d4458230d827e72e993f64dc1c","tid":1176488,"uid":147367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"一日mk妹"},{"pid":"e276eac110dd6e237af61b4ee5b780b188b90c46","tid":1176488,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"「越不洗臉皮膚越好」、「越吃消夜就越瘦」<br />\n<br />\n到底點先講得出咁D說話,佢外星人??=.="},{"pid":"6a92ed38d5eea34e1ba2ccf4c8a57bb55ef16892","tid":1176488,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"乜佢有好過<img src=\"/assets/